                       },
                       {
                           "index":  6,
                           "kind":  "outline-heading",
                           "text":  "1.1 研究背景",
                           "style":  "正文",
                           "outlineLevel":  2,
                           "fontName":  "",
                           "fontNameAscii":  "Times New Roman",
                           "fontSize":  14,
                           "bold":  -1,
                           "italic":  0,
                           "color":  -16777216,
                           "shading":  -16777216,
                           "alignment":  "0",
                           "leftIndent":  0,
                           "firstLineIndent":  0,
                           "lineSpacing":  22,
                           "spaceBefore":  6,
                           "spaceAfter":  3
                       },
                       {
                           "index":  7,
                           "kind":  "body",
                           "text":  "随着学术规范对文档格式要求的日益严格，确保文字处理软件能准确渲染标准格式成为关键需求。硕士论文结构复杂，包含大量层级标题、表格、公式及引用，其格式一致性直接影响学术成果的呈现与评审。WPS作为主流办公软件，其渲染引擎对GB/T 7713.1-2025等国家标准的支持程度，需要通过",
                           "style":  "正文",
                           "outlineLevel":  10,
                           "fontName":  "",
                           "fontNameAscii":  "Times New Roman",
                           "fontSize":  12,
                           "bold":  0,
                           "italic":  0,
                           "color":  -16777216,
                           "shading":  -16777216,
                           "alignment":  "3",
                           "leftIndent":  0,
                           "firstLineIndent":  2,
                           "lineSpacing":  20,
                           "spaceBefore":  0,
                           "spaceAfter":  0
                       },
                       {
                           "index":  8,
                           "kind":  "outline-heading",
                           "text":  "1.1.1 研究问题",
                           "style":  "正文",
                           "outlineLevel":  3,
                           "fontName":  "",
                           "fontNameAscii":  "Times New Roman",
                           "fontSize":  12,
                           "bold":  -1,
                           "italic":  0,
                           "color":  -16777216,
                           "shading":  -16777216,
                           "alignment":  "0",
                           "leftIndent":  0,
                           "firstLineIndent":  0,
                           "lineSpacing":  22,
                           "spaceBefore":  6,
                           "spaceAfter":  3
                       },
                       {
                           "index":  9,
                           "kind":  "body",
                           "text":  "本研究核心问题是：WPS能否在自动编号系统中正确处理用户手动插入的编号（如“1.1.1”）而不产生重复或冲突？此外，软件对块级公式、多语言摘要、特定表题图题格式的渲染是否完全符合规范？这些问题的答案依赖于设计覆盖全要素的回归测试用例。",
                           "style":  "正文",
                           "outlineLevel":  10,
                           "fontName":  "",
                           "fontNameAscii":  "Times New Roman",
                           "fontSize":  12,
                           "bold":  0,
                           "italic":  0,
                           "color":  -16777216,
                           "shading":  -16777216,
                           "alignment":  "3",
                           "leftIndent":  0,
                           "firstLineIndent":  2,
                           "lineSpacing":  20,
                           "spaceBefore":  0,
                           "spaceAfter":  0
                       },
                       {
                           "index":  10,
                           "kind":  "outline-heading",
                           "text":  "1.1.2 研究意义",
                           "style":  "正文",
                           "outlineLevel":  3,
                           "fontName":  "",
                           "fontNameAscii":  "Times New Roman",
                           "fontSize":  12,
                           "bold":  -1,
                           "italic":  0,
                           "color":  -16777216,
                           "shading":  -16777216,
                           "alignment":  "0",
                           "leftIndent":  0,
                           "firstLineIndent":  0,
                           "lineSpacing":  22,
                           "spaceBefore":  6,
                           "spaceAfter":  3
                       },
                       {
                           "index":  11,
                           "kind":  "outline-heading",
                           "text":  "通过构建标准化的硕士论文Markdown骨架进行渲染测试，可以量化评估WPS的格式兼容性。成功通过测试将增强用户对WPS处理学术文档的信心，失败则能精准定位渲染缺陷，为软件迭代提供明确目标。同时，该骨架本身可作为高校或期刊社的格式检查模板。",
                           "style":  "正文",
                           "outlineLevel":  3,
                           "fontName":  "",
                           "fontNameAscii":  "Times New Roman",
                           "fontSize":  12,
                           "bold":  0,
                           "italic":  0,
                           "color":  -16777216,
                           "shading":  -16777216,
