                       },
                       {
                           "index":  13,
                           "kind":  "outline-heading",
                           "text":  "2.1 渲染链路",
                           "style":  "正文",
                           "outlineLevel":  2,
                           "fontName":  "",
                           "fontNameAscii":  "Times New Roman",
                           "fontSize":  14,
                           "bold":  -1,
                           "italic":  0,
                           "color":  -16777216,
                           "shading":  -16777216,
                           "alignment":  "0",
                           "leftIndent":  0,
                           "firstLineIndent":  0,
                           "lineSpacing":  22,
                           "spaceBefore":  6,
                           "spaceAfter":  3
                       },
                       {
                           "index":  14,
                           "kind":  "outline-heading",
                           "text":  "测试设计的渲染链路模拟了从Markdown源码输入到最终PDF/页面输出的全过程。关键节点包括：解析器处理标题层级与手写编号、布局引擎计算表格与图表浮动位置、字体引擎匹配学术字符（如公式符号）、以及输出生成器应用页面样式。测试用例需针对每个节点注入边界条件。",
                           "style":  "正文",
                           "outlineLevel":  3,
                           "fontName":  "",
                           "fontNameAscii":  "Times New Roman",
                           "fontSize":  12,
                           "bold":  0,
                           "italic":  0,
                           "color":  -16777216,
                           "shading":  -16777216,
                           "alignment":  "3",
                           "leftIndent":  0,
                           "firstLineIndent":  2,
                           "lineSpacing":  20,
                           "spaceBefore":  0,
                           "spaceAfter":  0
                       },
                       {
                           "index":  15,
                           "kind":  "outline-heading",
                           "text":  "This sentence contains bold text, italic text, and inlineCode. 在回归测试中，必须确保这些基础内联元素在复杂文档结构中不被意外破坏或样式丢失。例如，在表格单元格或图注中，加粗和斜体应保持原义，代码片段应使用等宽字体。",
                           "style":  "正文",
                           "outlineLevel":  3,
                           "fontName":  "",
                           "fontNameAscii":  "",
                           "fontSize":  12,
                           "bold":  9999999,
                           "italic":  9999999,
                           "color":  -16777216,
                           "shading":  -16777216,
                           "alignment":  "3",
                           "leftIndent":  0,
                           "firstLineIndent":  2,
                           "lineSpacing":  20,
                           "spaceBefore":  0,
                           "spaceAfter":  0
                       },
                       {
                           "index":  16,
                           "kind":  "outline-heading",
                           "text":  "正文章节的自动编号逻辑是测试重点。当遇到“## 研究背景”时，系统应生成“1.1”；而遇到“### 1.1.1 研究问题”时，应原样保留“1.1.1”并继续后续 numbering 为“1.1.2”。这种混合编号模式常见于用户自定义的详细章节，考验渲染器的灵活性。",
                           "style":  "正文",
                           "outlineLevel":  3,
                           "fontName":  "",
                           "fontNameAscii":  "Times New Roman",
                           "fontSize":  12,
                           "bold":  0,
                           "italic":  0,
